{"tid":2064361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"維基百科有梁凌杰的條目，大家可以抽時間睇下","createTime":"2020-06-14T17:40:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T02:38:16.000Z","uid":71237,"like":140,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"27e01d08b975bcdcb28c9ad7acae790f3c7885de","tid":2064361,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T17:40:28.000Z","msg":"有一班巴打一直喺維基百科默默努力，去記載反送中運動的人物和事件。<br />\n梁凌杰更加喺最近當選維基百科的優良條目。大家如果想了解多啲梁凌杰，可以用少少時間去睇下。<br />\n<a href=\"https://w.wiki/7Va\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fw.wiki%2F7Va&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8vSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=bb7fd884\" target=\"_blank\">https://w.wiki/7Va</a>"},{"pid":"e5798a31d72215c13e1e98fe3491e033f86efea1","tid":2064361,"uid":71237,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T17:40:39.000Z","msg":"如果你都想喺維基百科寫嘢，喺寫之前不妨睇下我們提供的新手教學。<br />\n因為維基百科的特徵就係任何人都可以修改，好多人擔心自己寫嘅嘢會俾五毛亂刪。<br />\n但其實只要你花半個鐘時間去了解咗基本規則，你就會知道點樣寫先唔會輕易被刪除。<br />\n（相反如果你唔了解基本規則，你寫嘅嘢太差勁，就算我係同路人都會想刪除你寫嘅嘢。）<br />\n<br />\n目前維基百科活躍寫反送中運動嘅香港人大概只有十幾個，人手真係嚴重不足。<br />\n我們需要更多新血加入，多你一個就真係好多。好多嘢你唔寫就真係永遠無人寫。<br />\n<br />\n如果你係新手，可以閱讀以下的新手教學：<br />\n維基百科戰線招募長期參與者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1789084/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1789084/page/1</a><br />\n[教學] 如何成為維基百科撰寫師？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1595959/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1595959/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n如果你喺維基百科遇到問題，可以入telegram group搵其他資深維基人協助。<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/J3cWeBaQbYp1etQ4MOBLFw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FJ3cWeBaQbYp1etQ4MOBLFw&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8vSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=c5c47fcc\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/J3cWeBaQbYp1etQ4MOBLFw</a><br />\n<br />\n如果你想幫手寫嘢/做資料搜集，可以入telegram channel，睇下有咩條目需要幫手。<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAE8nDMP5qEHzdgBBQQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAE8nDMP5qEHzdgBBQQ&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8vSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=2ab182d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAE8nDMP5qEHzdgBBQQ</a><br />\n<br />\n如果你用手機寫緊維基百科，覺得要引用資料好麻煩，可以用「維基百科引用助手 Bot」<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkwikiref_bot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkwikiref_bot&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8vSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=4e7ad461\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkwikiref_bot</a><br />\n<br />\n如果大家發現維基百科有嘢值得寫/有惡意破壞，可以用維基百科(Wikipedia)報料Bot向我地報告。<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/wikiscout_bot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fwikiscout_bot&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8vSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=ebf4c105\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/wikiscout_bot</a><br />\n<br />\n如果你想了解關於維基百科戰線的最新消息，可以like我地的Facebook page。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E7%B6%AD%E5%9F%BA%E7%99%BE%E7%A7%91%E6%88%B0%E7%B7%9A-103027814743750/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E5%259F%25BA%25E7%2599%25BE%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2588%25B0%25E7%25B7%259A-103027814743750%2F&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8vSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=ffb62f3e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E7%B6%AD%E5%9F%BA%E7%99%BE%E7%A7%91%E6%88%B0%E7%B7%9A-103027814743750/</a><br />\n<br />\n維基百科戰線運作示意圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WY1G6ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWY1G6ad.jpg&h=93cc57c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f5220e14ee19fee72bfb7180174b972f981c8081","tid":2064361,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T17:43:18.000Z","msg":"good"},{"pid":"356cda817db9b0fbe76201a6d65ccfabf3949844","tid":2064361,"uid":244818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27e01d08b975bcdcb28c9ad7acae790f3c7885de","tid":2064361,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T17:40:28.000Z","msg":"有一班巴打一直喺維基百科默默努力，去記載反送中運動的人物和事件。<br />\n梁凌杰更加喺最近當選維基百科的優良條目。大家如果想了解多啲梁凌杰，可以用少少時間去睇下。<br />\n<a href=\"https://w.wiki/7Va\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fw.wiki%2F7Va&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8vSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=bb7fd884\" target=\"_blank\">https://w.wiki/7Va</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T17:43:58.000Z","msg":"wiki短link係點整？"},{"pid":"9f395a1d99bc5471c55063fbf9dfa9619be3476b","tid":2064361,"uid":24457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T17:45:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e512bbfd0359412f1a4fb3cd582eee07f40df61b","tid":2064361,"uid":24457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T17:46:37.000Z","msg":"好似本身個頁面會喺忌日show出嚟 但比人搞到無咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ca0b30f330f61fd41642b885e5cac453270db5b","tid":2064361,"uid":71237,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T17:47:37.000Z","msg":"同埋維基百科戰線都需要宣傳師。<br />\n各位可唔可以幫手去唔同的渠道分享依個post，希望可以吸引到更多唔同background嘅人留意到維基百科戰線。<br />\n<br />\n因為我喺連登推post都已經推咗半年有多，但係都幾乎無人加入，我覺得喺連登宣傳已經去到盡頭。<br />\n我希望有宣傳師可以協助，呼籲更多人加入維基百科戰線。<br />\n（唔需要文筆叻，識得整合唔同新聞報導，用自己文字寫返出嚟就得。）"},{"pid":"1379e5ec1981192c4b8040c12fb13fee825451c7","tid":2064361,"uid":231234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T17:47:55.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c4f673487a1451830ef67bbd1852fa0127de7efe","tid":2064361,"uid":133743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T17:48:10.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"d26627657afd1710d20ed7675869255a638d6e45","tid":2064361,"uid":71237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"356cda817db9b0fbe76201a6d65ccfabf3949844","tid":2064361,"uid":244818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27e01d08b975bcdcb28c9ad7acae790f3c7885de","tid":2064361,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T17:40:28.000Z","msg":"有一班巴打一直喺維基百科默默努力，去記載反送中運動的人物和事件。<br />\n梁凌杰更加喺最近當選維基百科的優良條目。大家如果想了解多啲梁凌杰，可以用少少時間去睇下。<br />\n<a href=\"https://w.wiki/7Va\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fw.wiki%2F7Va&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8vSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=bb7fd884\" target=\"_blank\">https://w.wiki/7Va</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T17:43:58.000Z","msg":"wiki短link係點整？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T17:48:18.000Z","msg":"最左手面有「短網址」"},{"pid":"09c9823c784f26e0d87dc01fec4c2e3bd92b560b","tid":2064361,"uid":71237,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e512bbfd0359412f1a4fb3cd582eee07f40df61b","tid":2064361,"uid":24457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T17:46:37.000Z","msg":"好似本身個頁面會喺忌日show出嚟 但比人搞到無咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T17:55:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bef438b47d3ff715bc0cbc9a0f5c0b1a6f85afbe","tid":2064361,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T17:55:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf49df38154e34110480536657fce3c0c5108ccf","tid":2064361,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T18:07:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"15748f5cd16bb817176f090f367bc24bf3ae7ccf","tid":2064361,"uid":321194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T18:08:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"488c1056a76a7061408df8cc18b6c866e01cdaaa","tid":2064361,"uid":55956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T18:10:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/pig.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/pig.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/pig.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/flower.gif\" class=\