aces/rip/mouse.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d9905728c7700708250fffe5f051d69120445a3","tid":2064361,"uid":223643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T04:41:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/mouse.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/mouse.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a149010d69cbb4c94b6d87679c1a6b8f79451dc6","tid":2064361,"uid":223643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5798a31d72215c13e1e98fe3491e033f86efea1","tid":2064361,"uid":71237,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T17:40:39.000Z","msg":"如果你都想喺維基百科寫嘢，喺寫之前不妨睇下我們提供的新手教學。<br />\n因為維基百科的特徵就係任何人都可以修改，好多人擔心自己寫嘅嘢會俾五毛亂刪。<br />\n但其實只要你花半個鐘時間去了解咗基本規則，你就會知道點樣寫先唔會輕易被刪除。<br />\n（相反如果你唔了解基本規則，你寫嘅嘢太差勁，就算我係同路人都會想刪除你寫嘅嘢。）<br />\n<br />\n目前維基百科活躍寫反送中運動嘅香港人大概只有十幾個，人手真係嚴重不足。<br />\n我們需要更多新血加入，多你一個就真係好多。好多嘢你唔寫就真係永遠無人寫。<br />\n<br />\n如果你係新手，可以閱讀以下的新手教學：<br />\n維基百科戰線招募長期參與者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1789084/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1789084/page/1</a><br />\n[教學] 如何成為維基百科撰寫師？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1595959/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1595959/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n如果你喺維基百科遇到問題，可以入telegram group搵其他資深維基人協助。<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/J3cWeBaQbYp1etQ4MOBLFw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FJ3cWeBaQbYp1etQ4MOBLFw&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8vSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=c5c47fcc\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/J3cWeBaQbYp1etQ4MOBLFw</a><br />\n<br />\n如果你想幫手寫嘢/做資料搜集，可以入telegram channel，睇下有咩條目需要幫手。<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAE8nDMP5qEHzdgBBQQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAE8nDMP5qEHzdgBBQQ&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8vSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=2ab182d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAE8nDMP5qEHzdgBBQQ</a><br />\n<br />\n如果你用手機寫緊維基百科，覺得要引用資料好麻煩，可以用「維基百科引用助手 Bot」<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkwikiref_bot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkwikiref_bot&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8vSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=4e7ad461\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkwikiref_bot</a><br />\n<br />\n如果大家發現維基百科有嘢值得寫/有惡意破壞，可以用維基百科(Wikipedia)報料Bot向我地報告。<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/wikiscout_bot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fwikiscout_bot&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8vSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=ebf4c105\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/wikiscout_bot</a><br />\n<br />\n如果你想了解關於維基百科戰線的最新消息，可以like我地的Facebook page。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E7%B6%AD%E5%9F%BA%E7%99%BE%E7%A7%91%E6%88%B0%E7%B7%9A-103027814743750/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E5%259F%25BA%25E7%2599%25BE%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2588%25B0%25E7%25B7%259A-103027814743750%2F&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8vSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=ffb62f3e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E7%B6%AD%E5%9F%BA%E7%99%BE%E7%A7%91%E6%88%B0%E7%B7%9A-103027814743750/</a><br />\n<br />\n維基百科戰線運作示意圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WY1G6ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWY1G6ad.jpg&h=93cc57c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T04:42:12.000Z","msg":"謝謝"},{"pid":"f7fbdad2e15655b4f309b7c7e60557955baf9568","tid":2064361,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T05:11:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"23626b2d5d237f5550716e62f7e393955a2197c4","tid":2064361,"uid":150610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T05:12:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ec9cdb1a29156be83f22a0fe9c0480d8d86bdb14","tid":2064361,"uid":9824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T05:18:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c2ca66c529c74cf1fffe56de7166dc1457e2c9e9","tid":2064361,"uid":40055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T05:27:41.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"6c740