拘捕，當時正在擔保外出，又指梁無業、經常沉迷電腦遊戲[5]。<br />\n<br />\n《點新聞》報導指有網上傳言聲稱梁凌杰最後接觸者為鄺俊宇，兩人對話內容涉及銀行過數問題，又稱鄺在現場致電梁教他「跳下去氣墊，讓多一點傳媒拍攝到」[18]。鄺俊宇回應指《點新聞》「行為卑鄙、可恥、違反道德」，猶如「踩著死者屍體去作新聞」[55]，要求立即撤回及刪除有關報道，並保留追究權利[56]。《自由時報》在同日的報導中查證指，《點新聞》網站及專頁已無法找到該篇報導[57]<br />\n<br />\n呢兩檔仆街野D審編真係要落地獄.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b9faf44fac2549a3df1f713eca6cb34cc744197","tid":2064361,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T10:06:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c78e0530119138490b4ac6b637c91231dd3a22ac","tid":2064361,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T14:02:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f0bb791fdf66a7d40caa93bdbc90afe0c4d075b1","tid":2064361,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T15:01:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f83f5c376449cecac4ce62ad599ba7d61ee002b9","tid":2064361,"uid":24707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T15:02:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/flower.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b983543a66d990686bf6148bc2d75f750ee5709","tid":2064361,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T16:08:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"77c92c1869b322da3391fb673a4b856c716e2657","tid":2064361,"uid":28960,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T16:13:04.000Z","msg":"寫得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f33c4eb483232a3a53c3b9d7e74d3bf17f395192","tid":2064361,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T17:08:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"32e08a5f8f1fd8ed9ad563a4ab627c79d785ee53","tid":2064361,"uid":151924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T17:12:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/pig.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"001727b7b548b71fe9c52316a225a08f8387c61d","tid":2064361,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep